name: welcome to my mind by domingos

metadata.name: be free
metadata.description: The freedom of wonder and imagination that a child possesses is truly a beautiful thing to behold. As they run through a grassy field, their laughter and joy echoing through the countryside, they hold tightly to a green helium-filled balloon, their eyes wide with wonder as they watch it dance and sway above them. The world around them is a canvas, waiting to be painted with their boundless creativity and curiosity. Each step they take is a brushstroke, each breath they take a burst of color. The grassy field, the green balloon, and the endless sky above all become a part of their masterpiece, a tapestry woven from the threads of their imagination. It is a privilege to witness the freedom of a child's mind, and to be reminded of the boundless potential that exists within each and every one of us.
